Gaggenau 24 inch Vario 200 series gas cooktop

A classic 60 cm wide gas cooktop with an output of 9.4 kW on four burners: two high-output burners and two standard-output burners for different types of cookware. Smooth-surface cast pan supports ensure hassle-free and safe moving of pots and pans. The generous control panel in aluminium or stainless steel provides convenient handling.

Cooking zones
-Two high-output burners (560 -2800 W 1900 – 9500 BTU).
-Two standard burners (380 – 1900 W 1300 – 6500 BTU).

Operation
-Control knob with ring and output marking.
-One-handed operation.
-Electric ignition of all burners.
-Gas valve with fine control.

Features
-Two-part pan support with flat continuous pot surface.
-Enameled burner caps.
